column4: NSLOCTEXT("[5ED035A04FF05BF344BF7BAAB0067FCC]", "24F89B434BEA821A8E1BC78958EBD032", "Have you heard? There is a strange plant growing in Tropical Jungle.")

NSLOCTEXT("[5ED035A04FF05BF344BF7BAAB0067FCC]", "E5ED04CA4456BDB58BDBFE8563FD7B58", "It bears fruit every year around the fifteenth. You may take those.")
